bbcb610f-1cce-435d-bc64-372c134fdc86.title: Shamus
bbcb610f-1cce-435d-bc64-372c134fdc86.text:
Ay yer big elephant! Yer've caught me, to be sure!
What would an elephant like yer be wanting wid ol'
Shamus then?

fbb19ff2-bde9-448f-92d2-1c85d013fbf9.title: Shamus
fbb19ff2-bde9-448f-92d2-1c85d013fbf9.text:
Well you'll have to be catchin' me again when yer are,
elephant!

37e19463-1e20-4f71-9c6f-76ed004ca843.title: Shamus
37e19463-1e20-4f71-9c6f-76ed004ca843.text:
Ay yer big elephant! Yer've caught me, to be sure!
What would an elephant like yer be wanting wid ol'
Shamus then?

eea9c3c4-df9c-4f3f-8bd8-41e82906ce4b.title: Shamus
eea9c3c4-df9c-4f3f-8bd8-41e82906ce4b.text:
Zanaris is it now? Well well well... Yer'll be needing to
be going to that funny little shed out there in the
swamp, so you will."

a549ca57-2cc7-4f78-a23c-d02ebc07c93f.title: <player>
a549ca57-2cc7-4f78-a23c-d02ebc07c93f.text: ...but... I thought... Zanaris was a city...?

options.text: How does it fit in a shed then?
I've been in that shed, I didn't see a city.

6b0286be-7d2c-4d0c-95d1-8e1a2190415e.title: <player>
6b0286be-7d2c-4d0c-95d1-8e1a2190415e.text: I've been in that shed. I didn't see a city.

fb30812f-e352-4568-98c0-552664e18778.title: Shamus
fb30812f-e352-4568-98c0-552664e18778.text:
Oh, was I fergetting to say? Yer need to be carrying a
Dramenwood staff to be getting there! Otherwise Yer'll
just be ending up in the shed.

f8bc130a-5581-40b5-9ef6-ef27271db6e3.title: <player>
f8bc130a-5581-40b5-9ef6-ef27271db6e3.text: So where would I get a staff?

aff6dc74-b0e6-4797-abcd-bf1bab812a8b.title: Shamus
aff6dc74-b0e6-4797-abcd-bf1bab812a8b.text:
Dramenwood staffs are crafted from branches of the
Dramen tree, so they are. I hear there's a Dramen
tree over on the island of Entrana in a cave

e7122acb-0223-49c5-9600-40a5191855c1.title: Shamus
e7122acb-0223-49c5-9600-40a5191855c1.text:
or some such. There would probably be a good place
for an elephant like yer to be starting looking I reckon.

70c8b125-5aa6-44db-a300-c4eb32fa399d.title: Shamus
70c8b125-5aa6-44db-a300-c4eb32fa399d.text:
The monks are running a ship from Port Sarim to
Entrana, I hear too. Now leave me alone yer elephant!

43af138e-670c-4629-8965-9d9f217b3be1.title: <player>
43af138e-670c-4629-8965-9d9f217b3be1.text: How does it fit in a shed then?

bf7d4801-c83b-41d0-90ce-b3296f4a4bcc.title: Shamus
bf7d4801-c83b-41d0-90ce-b3296f4a4bcc.text:
Ah yer stupid elephant! The city isn't IN the shed! The
doorway to the shed is being a portal to Zanaris, so it is.

8d794372-208b-4587-8c50-90f1563b8ec3.title: Shamus
8d794372-208b-4587-8c50-90f1563b8ec3.text:
Ay yer big elephant! Yer've caught me, to be sure!
What would an elephant like yer be wanting wid ol'
Shamus then?

options.text: How do I get to Zanaris again?

036ee43d-f0f1-468c-ba21-a70f4df21052.title: Shamus
036ee43d-f0f1-468c-ba21-a70f4df21052.text:
Ha! Look at yer! Look at the stupid elephant who tries to
go catching a leprechaun when he don't even be
 knowing what he wants!

f01c75aa-1994-4cea-855b-98985c74e30b.title: <player>
f01c75aa-1994-4cea-855b-98985c74e30b.text: How do I get to Zanaris again?

6929ab43-28f0-4561-bb28-93730fd22575.title: Shamus
6929ab43-28f0-4561-bb28-93730fd22575.text:
Yer stupid elephant! I'll tell yer again! Yer need to be
entering the shed in the middle of the swamp while
holding a dramenwood staff! Yer can make the
Dramen staff

7196d964-20f0-4009-b5af-9591d7657238.title: Shamus
7196d964-20f0-4009-b5af-9591d7657238.text:
from a dramen tree branch, and there's a Dramen tree on
Entrana! Now leave me alone yer great elephant!
